        "content": "We have the project structure. Next task is \"implement_sensor\" - implement capacitive soil moisture sensor driver with ADC reading and averaging. Need to decide specifics: The sensor is \"capacitive soil moisture level 1.2\" - likely an analog capacitive sensor that outputs 0-3.3V proportional to moisture. Use ADC1 on ESP32-S3. Use ADC attenuation 11db for 0-3.3V range. Read multiple samples and average. Provide method to get raw value and percentage.\n\nNext task is implement_sensor. Then implement_calibration, implement_display, implement_wifi. Let's do sensor now.",
